content.onValue:
switch (value) {
  case getIndex('Reaper'):
    send('/Reaper')
    break
  case getIndex('Mixer'):
    send('/Mixer')
    break
  case getIndex('Volcano'):
    send('/Volcano')
    break
  case getIndex('SSL'):
    send('/SSL')
    break
  case getIndex('Omni'):
    send('/Omni')
    break
  case getIndex('EQ'):
    send('/EQ')
    break
  case getIndex('Compressor'):
    send('/Compressor')
    break
  case getIndex('Saturn'):
    send('/Saturn')
    break
  case getIndex('Reverb'):
    send('/Reverb')
    break
  case getIndex('Limiter'):
    send('/Limiter')
    break
  case getIndex('ReaDelay'):
    send('/ReaDelay')
    break
  case getIndex('ReaComp'):
    send('/ReaComp')
    break
  case getIndex('ProMB'):
    send('/ProMB')
    break
  case getIndex('MidiEditor'):
    send('/MidiEditor')
    break
}
